description: The Kelani Froyo Truck is rolling up to curbs all over San Antonio with the best frozen yogurt around! Treats your sweet tooth will love, the frozen yogurt, shaved ice, and every other delicious delight are ready for the sunny Texas streets. Perfect for any occasion, Kelani Froyo Truck can make every day amazing, so keep your eyes peeled for this red and blue truck today!
name: Kelani Froyo Truck
